It seems to me that those who choose their fights are not really warriors but.. Perhaps, chicken shits!<br>
It is the little weak man who stands up to the bully and either kicks his ass or gets the shit stomped out of him that wins my admiration.<br>
It is the passer-by that intervenes to prevent the rape or severe beating of a stranger that gains my approval.<br>
It is the person who endeavors to avoid violence through debate, arbitration, compromise, logic and rational.. without prostituting himself that impresses me... because if the talk doesn't work, he will draw his sword...against any odds. <br>
It is the person who will fight anyone, anywhere at anytime not just to protect himself, his family and loved ones, his country, his flag, his way of life, his property but fights for beliefs...This type person who fights for himself because of deeply ingrained values.. is the type of person who will fight for the rights of all people.. at all times.<br>
Criminals (mostly chicken shits) pick their fights...Law officers respond to them.  Chicken shits start wars... Soldiers, Marines, Airmen, Sailors, Civilians respond to them.<br>
Chicken Shits who sit around after the fact and justify why they didn't fight... are Chicken Shits!<br>
Those who enter only tailor made fights where they are guaranteed the outcome... opportunity seekers... profit takers.. are not fighters, they are predators and cowards.<br>
Those who stand on a far away hill and shout at the fighters are the biggest Chicken Shits of all!<br>
You are not only a Chicken, Spatz.. You are a Chicken Shit.<br>
Perhaps it is inappropriate to call names.. But a Chicken Shit by any other name would still smell the same.<br>
There are people like Tom Dier who vote in an election and their candidate looses.  They have a right to bitch.<br>
There are people like Cook Barela who vote for a winner and they have a right to boast.<br>
Voters take a stand.<br>
There are those like Barry Spatz who do not take a stand... who have neither the right to boast or bitch... they are simply... Chicken Shits!<br>
Finally, there are people like Art, SW, and me who really don't bitch or boast too much.. We're just expert Chicken Shit inspectors!
